@endnode


@node Future

@{b}@{u}Future@{ub}@{uu}

 I have many ideas in mind for future versions of TrashIt.

 The most important thing is to completely revise the control panel. I ran out of room for new options a while ago, which is why some of the options aren't available on the control panel.

 After that, I would like to add some more options, an ARexx port, online AmigaGuide help, etc.

 However, I would love to hear your ideas for features that you would like to have. Feel free to @{" contact " link Author} me with any request you want, no matter how big or small. You can also @{" contact me" link Author} if you would like to be a @{" beta tester " link BetaTest}.
@endnode


@node BetaTest
@title "Beta Testers"

