@node History
@title "Revision History"

@{b}@{u}Revision History@{ub}@{uu}

 1.20		4.5.93		Current release.

 I fixed an error that was causing crashes when deleting files on machines with a 68040, added a few useful options (Delete Limit, undelete, empty trash when disk dropped), fixed an error that caused TrashIt to hang when it tried to play a sound but couldn't allocate the audio device, fixed an error that caused TrashIt to hang for some people when searching for trashcans on all volumes, and cleaned up a little here and there.


 1.20beta	4.2.93		Release to @{" beta testers " link BetaTest}.

 I revamped the code to be more modular, added clipboard support, improved deletion error handling, made the sound player a separate task, and added several other minor enhancements. I also found and removed several bugs.


 1.11		3.13.93		Internal release.

 There were no bugs reported by the @{" beta testers " link BetaTest}, but they did suggest quite a few minor enhancements, so I implemented them.


 1.1beta	2.4.93		Release to @{" beta testers " link BetaTest}.

 Too many improvements to list. Not one line of code survived from the old version.


 1.0		8.15.92		Initial release.

 Very simple, with no options, but didn't work very well.
@endnode
